name: src/cothority-protobuf.js
CothorityProtobuf
description:
Base class for the protobuf library that provides helpers to encode and decode
messages according to a given model

name: encodeMessage
description: Encode a model to be transmitted over websocket

name: decodeMessage
description: Decode a message coming from a websocket

name: getModel
description: Return the protobuf loaded model

name: src/index.js
CothorityMessages
description: Helpers to encode and decode messages of the Cothority

name: createSignatureRequest
description: Create an encoded message to make a sign request to a cothority node

params.name: message
params.description: Message to sign stored in a Uint8Array

name: decodeSignatureResponse
description: Return the decoded response of a signature request

name: decodeStatusResponse
description: Return the decoded response of a status request

name: createStoreSkipBlockRequest
description: Create a message to store a new block

params.name: id
params.description: ID of the current latest block

name: decodeStoreSkipBlockResponse
description: Return the decoded message of a store skip block request

name: createLatestBlockRequest
description: Create a message request to get the latest blocks of a skip-chain

params.name: id
params.description: ID of the genesis block of the skip-chain

name: decodeLatestBlockResponse
description: Return the decoded message of a latest block request

name: createRandomMessage
description: Create a message request to get a random number

name: decodeRandomResponse
description: Return the decoded message of a random number request

name: createPinRequest
description: Create an encoded message to make a PinRequest to a cothority node

name: createStoreConfig
description: Create an encoded message to store configuration information of a given PoP party

name: deccdeStoreConfigReply
description: Return the decoded response

name: createFinalizeRequest
description: Create an encoded message to finalize on the given descid-popconfig

name: decodeFinalizeResponse
description: Return the decoded response

name: createConfigUpdate
description: Create a message request to get the config of a given conode

name: decodeConfigUpdateReply
description: Return the decoded message of a config update

name: createDevice
description: Create a device structure, that may be added to a config

name: createProposeSend
description: Create a message request to propose an update to a config

name: createProposeUpdate
description: Create a message request to get the current config update propositions

name: decodeProposeUpdateReply
description: Return the decoded message of a propose update

name: createProposeVote
description: Create a message request to vote an update to a config

name: cothorityMessages
description: Singleton
